26quot%3BPetition%20DENIED%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERana%2C%2064%2C%20is%20currently%20detained%20at%20the%20Metropolitan%20Detention%20Center%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20the%20US%20government%20had%20argued%20in%20the%20court%20that%20the%20petition%20for%20a%20writ%20of%20certiorari%20should%20be%20denied.%20US%20Solicitor%20General%20Elizabeth%20B%20Prelogar%20said%20this%20in%20its%20filing%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20December%2016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20Rana%20was%20not%20entitled%20to%20relief%20from%20extradition%20to%20India%20in%20this%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20'petitions%20for%20a%20writ%20of%20certiorari%20to%20review%20the%20judgment%20of%20the%20United%20States%20Court%20of%20Appeals%20for%20the%20Ninth%20Circuit%2C%20Rana%20had%20argued%20that%20he%20was%20tried%20and%20acquitted%20in%20federal%20court%20in%20the%20Northern%20District%20of%20Illinois%20(Chicago)%20on%20charges%20relating%20to%20the%202008%20terrorist%20attack%20on%20Mumbai.%20%C2%A0%26quot%3BIndia%20now%20seeks%20to%20extradite%20him%20for%20trial%20on%20charges%20based%20on%20the%20identical%20conduct%20at%20issue%20in%20the%20Chicago%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrelogar%20disagreed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20government%20does%20not%20concede%20that%20all%20of%20the%20conduct%20on%20which%20India%20seeks%20extradition%20was%20covered%20by%20the%20government's%20prosecution%20in%20this%20case.%20%C2%A0For%20example%2C%20India's%20forgery%20charges%20are%20based%20in%20part%20on%20conduct%20that%20was%20not%20charged%20in%20the%20United%20States%3A%20petitioner's%20use%20of%20false%20information%20in%20an%20application%20to%20formally%20open%20a%20branch%20office%20of%20the%20Immigration%20Law%20Center%20submitted%20to%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20US%20Solicitor%20General%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20clear%20that%20the%20jury's%20verdict%20in%20this%20case-%20which%20involves%20conspiracy%20charges%20and%20was%20somewhat%20difficult%20to%20parse%20-%20means%20that%20he%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bconvicted%20or%20acquitted%26quot%3B%20on%20all%20of%20the%20specific%20conduct%20that%20India%20has%20charged%2C%26quot%3B%20Prelogar%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERana%20is%20known%20to%20be%20associated%20with%20Pakistani-American%20terrorist%20David%20Coleman%20Headley%2C%20one%20of%20the%20main%20conspirators%20of%20the%2026%2F11%20Mumbai%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%20166%20people%2C%20including%20six%20Americans%2C%20were%20killed%20in%20the%202008%20Mumbai%20terror%20attacks%20in%20which%2010%20Pakistani%20terrorists%20laid%20a%20more%20than%2060-hour%20siege%2C%20attacking%20and%20killing%20people%20at%20iconic%20and%20vital%20locations%20of%20Mumbai.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737777300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fik9apsg_tahawwur-rana-2008-mumbai-terror-attack-ani_625x300_17_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-supreme-court-clears-26-11-accused-tahawwur-ranas-extradition-to-india-7554096%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20cleared%20Mumbai-attack%20convict%20Tahawwur%20Rana's%20extradition%20to%20India%20as%20it%20dismissed%20a%20review%20petition%20against%20his%20conviction%20in%20the%20case.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-supreme-court-clears-26-11-accused-tahawwur-ranas-extradition-to-india-7554096%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump's%20Controversial%20Pick%20Pete%20Hegseth%20Confirmed%20As%20US%20Defence%20Secretary%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Senate%20narrowly%20confirmed%20former%20Fox%20News%20co-host%20Pete%20Hegseth%20as%20Pentagon%20chief%20on%20Friday%2C%20despite%20allegations%20of%20alcohol%20abuse%2C%20sexual%20misconduct%20and%20other%20fears%20about%20his%20ability%20to%20lead%20the%20world's%20most%20powerful%20military.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20Republican%20senators%20voted%20against%20Donald%20Trump's%20pick%20as%20secretary%20of%20defense%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%2050-50%20tie%20that%20required%20JD%20Vance%20to%20cast%20the%20deciding%20ballot%20--%20only%20the%20second%20time%20in%20history%20a%20vice%20president%20has%20had%20to%20intervene%20to%20save%20a%20cabinet%20nominee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20razor-edged%20result%20underscored%20concerns%20about%20Hegseth%2C%20who%20will%20take%20over%20the%20Pentagon%20with%20war%20raging%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20the%20Middle%20East%20volatile%20despite%20ceasefires%20in%20Lebanon%20and%20Gaza%2C%20and%20as%20Trump%20expands%20the%20military's%20role%20in%20security%20on%20the%20US-Mexico%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2044-year-old%20is%20a%20former%20Army%20National%20Guard%20officer%20who%20until%20recently%20worked%20as%20a%20co-host%20for%20Fox%20News%20--%20one%20of%20Trump's%20favored%20television%20channels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHegseth%20has%20a%20combative%20media%20personality%2C%20fierce%20loyalty%20and%20telegenic%20looks%20--%20common%20hallmarks%20in%20Trump's%20entourage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESupporters%20say%20Hegseth's%20deployments%20in%20Afghanistan%20and%20Iraq%20give%20him%20the%20insight%20to%20run%20the%20Defense%20Department%20better%20than%20more%20experienced%20officials%20who%20would%20normally%20be%20considered%20for%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20pledged%20to%20focus%20the%20military%20on%20%26quot%3Blethality%26quot%3B%20and%20to%20bring%20back%20%26quot%3Bwarrior%20culture%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20Pentagon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20confir