l%20abuse%20problem%20and%20was%20abusive%20to%20his%20ex-wife%20Samantha%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20affidavit%20said%2C%20though%20it%20noted%20that%20Danielle%20Hegseth%20did%20not%20personally%20witness%20physical%20or%20sexual%20abuse%20by%20the%20incoming%20defense%20secretary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDanielle%20Hegseth%20however%20said%20she%20%26quot%3Bpersonally%20observed...%20Hegseth's%20erratic%20and%20aggressive%20behavior%20over%20many%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20that%20she%20was%20subjected%20to%20emotional%20abuse%20by%20him%2C%20and%20that%20she%20was%20told%20by%20his%20ex-wife%20that%20she%20once%20hid%20from%20him%20in%20a%20closet%20because%20she%20%26quot%3Bfeared%20for%20her%20personal%20safety.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20affidavit%2C%20Hegseth%20also%20told%20his%20ex-sister-in-law%20that%20women%20should%20not%20work%20or%20have%20the%20right%20to%20vote%2C%20and%20said%20that%20%26quot%3BChristians%20needed%20to%20have%20more%20children%20so%20they%20can%20overtake%20the%20Muslim%20population.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20combative%20confirmation%20hearing%2C%20Hegseth%20stuck%20to%20his%20opposition%20to%20diversity%2C%20equity%20and%20inclusion%20policies%20--%20long%20a%20bugbear%20for%20Republicans%20--%20saying%20they%20are%20%26quot%3Bdividing%20troops%20inside%20formations%2C%20causing%20commanders%20to%20walk%20on%20eggshells%2C%20not%20putting%20meritocracy%20first.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20sought%20to%20soften%20past%20remarks%20opposing%20women%20serving%20in%20combat%2C%20telling%20lawmakers%20that%20%26quot%3Bwomen%20will%20have%20access%20to%20ground%20combat%20roles...%20given%20the%20standards%20remain%20high.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20more%20of%20Trump's%20most%20contentious%20nominees%20will%20soon%20be%20grilled%20by%20lawmakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKash%20Patel%20--%20Trump's%20nominee%20to%20lead%20the%20FBI%20--%20Tulsi%20Gabbard%2C%20his%20pick%20for%20director%20o