ighborhood%20kids%20by%20growling%20%E2%80%9CGet%20off%20my%20lawn!%E2%80%9D%20anytime%20an%20oblivious%20child%20stepped%20foot%20on%20their%20precious%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Peter%20Debruge%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2025%2Ffilm%2Freviews%2Fthe-perfect-neighbor-review-1236285445%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Budget%202025%3A%20How%20Married%20Couples%20Could%20Benefit%20From%20Joint%20Tax%20Filing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20Union%20Budget%202025%2C%20the%20Institute%20of%20Chartered%20Accountants%20of%20India%20(ICAI)%20has%20proposed%20the%20introduction%20of%20joint%20taxation%20for%20married%20couples.%20Under%20joint%20taxation%2C%20a%20married%20couple%20would%20be%20treated%20as%20a%20single%20taxable%20unit%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20combine%20their%20incomes%20when%20filing%20tax%20returns%2C%20similar%20to%20systems%20already%20in%20place%20in%20countries%20like%20the%20US%20and%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BICAI%20suggests%20allowing%20joint%20income%20tax%20return%20filing%20for%20married%20couples%2C%26quot%3B%20Chartered%20Accountant%20Chirag%20Chauhan%20wrote%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%20%26quot%3BIdeally%2C%20an%20individual%20income%20of%20Rs%207%20lakh%20is%20exempt%20from%20tax%3B%20if%20married%2C%20the%20exempt%20limit%20for%20the%20family%20would%20be%20Rs%2014%20lakh.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EICAI%20suggests%20allowing%20joint%20income%20tax%20return%20filing%20for%20married%20couples.%20Ideally%2C%20an%20individual%20income%20of%20%E2%82%B97%20lakh%20is%20exempt%20from%20tax%3B%20if%20married%2C%20the%20exempt%20limit%20for%20the%20family%20would%20be%20%E2%82%B914%20lakh.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnWill%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2Fbudget2025%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23budget2025%3C%2Fa%3E%20introduce%20this%20new%20concept%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20CA%20Chirag%20Chauhan%20(%40CAChirag)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCAChirag%2Fstatus%2F1876588595810849196%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%207%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20the%20proposal%20suggests%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ICAI%20suggests%20that%20married%20couples%20should%20be%20able%20to%20choose%20between%20filing%20taxes%20individually%20or%20together%20under%20a%20new%20joint%20taxation%20system.%20This%20system%20could%20benefit%20families%20with%20one%20income%20earner%20and%20help%20prevent%20tax%20avoidance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20proposed%20tax%20slabs%20for%20couples%20filing%20jointly%20are%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUp%20to%20Rs%206%20lakh%3A%20No%20tax%3Cbr%3E%5CnRs%206-14%20lakh%3A%205%20per%20cent%20tax%3Cbr%3E%5CnRs%2014-20%20lakh%3A%2010%20per%20cent%20tax%3Cbr%3E%5CnRs%2020-24%20lakh%3A%2015%20per%20cent%20tax%3Cbr%3E%5CnRs%2024-30%20lakh%3A%2020%20per%20cent%20tax%3Cbr%3E%5CnAbove%20Rs%2030%20lakh%3A%2030%20per%20cent%20tax%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20joint%20filing%20system%2C%20the%20basic%20exemption%20limit%20would%20be%20doubled%20to%20Rs%206%20lakh%20from%20the%20current%20Rs%203%20lakh.%20The%20ICAI%20also%20recommends%20raising%20the%20surcharge%20threshold%20from%20Rs%2050%20lakh%20to%20Rs%201%20crore.%20The%20surcharge%20would%20apply%20as%20follows%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERs%201%20crore%20to%20Rs%202%20crore%3A%2010%20per%20cent%20surcharge%3Cbr%3E%5CnRs%202%20crore%20to%20Rs%204%20crore%3A%2015%20per%20cent%20surcharge%3Cbr%3E%5CnAbove%20Rs%204%20crore%3A%2025%20per%20cent%20surcharge%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20partners%20in%20a%20salaried%20couple%20would%20also%20benefit%20from%20the%20standard%20deduction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECurrent%20tax%20system%20for%20married%20couples%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20married%20couples%20in%20India%20file%20taxes%20separately%2C%20which%20can%20lead%20to%20higher%20taxes%20when%20one%20spouse%20earns%20more%20than%20the%20other.%20The%20system%20works%20better%20for%20families%20where%20both%20partners%20earn%2C%20as%20they%20can%20each%20claim%20deductions%20individually.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20single-income%20families%20miss%20out%20on%20these%20benefits.%20In%20countries%20like%20the%20USA%2C%20joint%20filing%20reduces%20the%20overall%20tax%20burden%20by%20combining%20incomes%20and%20offering%20extra%20deductions%20and%20credits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ICAI%20has%20also%20raised%20concerns%20that%20the%20current%20basic%20exemption%20limit%20is%20insufficient%20considering%20the%20cost%20of%20living.%20It%20has%20been%20suggested%20that%20families%20should%20look%20into%20shifting%20income%20to%20other%20members%20to%20reduce%20tax%20obligations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20joint%20taxation%20system%20can%20work%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20choosing%20joint%20filing%2C%20families%20can%20significantly%20lower%20their%20tax%20liability%20through%20additional%20deductions%20and%20more%20favourable%20tax%20rates%20compared%20to%20filing%20separately.%20This%20system%20helps%20reduce%20the%20overall%20tax%20burden%20for%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EExpert%20opinion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETax%20experts%20think%20it%20is%20unlikely%20to%20be%20implemented%20in%20the%20upcoming%20budget.%C2%A0%26quot%3BWhile%20joint%20taxation%20will%20be%20a%20beneficial%20move%2C%20the%20government%20may%20take%20time%20to%20introduce%20such%20a%20scheme%20as%20it%20would%20require%20the%20introduction%20of%20a%20completely%20new%20regime%20with%20different%20slabs%20and%20rates%2C%20deductions%2C%20exemptions%2C%20surcharges%2C%20etc.%20Hence%2C%20it%20is%20uncertain%20if%20such%20a%20scheme%20will%20be%20introduced%20in%20the%20upcoming%20budget%2C%26quot%3B%20SR%20Patnaik%2C%20partner%2C%20and%20head%20of%20taxation%20at%20Cyril%20Amarchand%20Mangaldas%2C%20a%20law%20firm%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fupstox.com%2Fnews%2Fpersonal-finance%2Ftax%2Fjoint-taxation-of-married-couples-in-india-why-budget-2025-may-not-follow-the-us-and-uk-model%2Farticle-140940%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUpstox%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECA%20Suresh%20Surana%20explained%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businesstoday.in%2Funion-budget%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fstory%2Fbudget-2025-joint-taxation-for-married-couples-can-be-a-gamechanger-how-will-this-work-460226-2025-01-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Today%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20ICAI's%20proposal%20is%20meant%20to%20help%20families%2C%20especially%20when%20one%20spouse%20is%20the%20main%20earner.%20He%20explained%20that%20people%20can%20choose%20between%20the%20default%20tax%20system%20and%20the%20regular%20tax%20rules.%20The%20basic%20exemption%20limit%20for%20individuals%20is%20Rs%202.5%20lakh%20under%20the%20default%20system%2C%20but%20it%20could%20increase%20to%20Rs%203%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737776460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fmi7bn5ug_calculator-generic-tax-generic-unsplash_625x300_25_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbudget-2025-icai-proposes-joint-tax-filing-how-married-couples-will-benefit-from-it-7516790%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ahead%20of%20the%20Union%20Budget%202025%2C%20the%20Institute%20of%20Chartered%20Accountants%20of%20India%20(ICAI)%20has%20proposed%20the%20introduction%20of%20joint%20taxation%20for%20married%20couples.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20suspends%20most%20foreign%20a