%20Post%2FThe%20Washington%20Post%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPete%20Hegseth%20has%20been%20confirmed%20as%20defense%20secretary%20after%20a%20tie-breaking%20vote%20by%20JD%20Vance.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20outspoken%20Army%20National%20Guard%20veteran%20and%20former%20Fox%20News%20host%20faced%20major%20controversies.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHegseth's%20confirmation%20suggests%20major%20changes%20may%20be%20in%20store%20for%20the%20Pentagon.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EVice%20President%20JD%20Vance%20on%20Friday%20delivered%20his%20first%20tie-breaking%20vote%20in%20the%20senate%2C%20confirming%20Pete%20Hegseth%2C%20a%20Trump%20confidant%20and%20Iraq%20veteran%2C%20as%20defense%20secretary%20after%20a%20contentious%20battle%20over%20his%20qualifications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDemocrats%20and%20three%20Republicans%20questioned%20Hegseth's%20readiness%20to%20lead%20the%20Pentagon%2C%20as%20the%20US%20Army%20National%20Guard%20veteran%20and%20former%20%26quot%3BFox%20%26amp%3B%20Friends%26quot%3B%20host%20lacks%20experience%20in%20the%20defense%20industry%20or%20running%20large%20organizations%20that%20have%20characterized%20past%20defense%20secretaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHegseth%20was%20barely%20confirmed%20on%20Friday%20night%20after%20a%2050-50%20Senate%20vote%2C%20which%20required%20a%20tie-breaking%20vote%20by%20Vance.%20Republican%20Senators%20Mitch%20McConnell%20from%20Kentucky%2C%20Susan%20Collins%20from%20Maine%2C%20and%20Lisa%20Murkowski%20from%20Alaska%20voted%20against%20Hegseth.%20All%20Democratic%20senators%20voted%20no.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20confirmation%20was%20only%20the%20second%20time%20in%20US%20history%20that%20the%20Vice%20President%20has%20been%20required%20to%20break%20a%20tie%20for%20a%20cabinet%20appointment.%20The%20first%20was%20Betsy%20DeVos'%202017%20confirmation%20as%20secretary%20of%20education%20during%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20first%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHegseth's%20confirmation%20is%20one%20of%20the%20closest%20ever%20for%20the%20position%2C%20which%20has%20often%20seen%20strong%20bipartisan%20support.%20For%20comparison%2C%20Lloyd%20Austin%2C%20a%20retired%20Army%20general%20tapped%20by%20former%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EPresident%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20received%2093%20votes%20in%202021.%20In%20addition%20to%20Hegseth%2C%20one%20of%20the%20other%20closest%20votes%20occurred%20in%202013%2C%20when%20the%20Senate%20confirmed%20former%20President%20Barack%20Obama's%20pick%2C%20Chuck%20Hagel%2C%20a%20former%20Republican%20senator%20and%20Vietnam%20combat%20veteran%2C%20by%2058-41.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHegseth's%20nail-bitter%20confirmation%20in%20the%20GOP-led%20Senate%20is%20a%20victory%20for%20Trump's%20unconventional%20Cabinet%20nominations.%20Since%20Trump%20announced%20his%20pick%20in%20November%2C%20Hegseth's%20personal%20history%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpete-hegseth-backs-trump-plans-for-military-covid-vaccine-refusers-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econtroversial%20comments%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20culture%20war%20topics%2C%20and%20qualifications%20for%20the%20position%20have%20all%20been%20under%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Fox%20News%20host's%20confirmation%20hearing%20in%20January%2C%20he%20faced%20intense%20questioning%2C%20walking%20back%20previous%20comments%20he%20made%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrumps-pentagon-pick-walked-back-his-outspoken-opposition-to-women-in-combat-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eagainst%20women%20serving%20in%20combat%20roles%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20promising%20to%20bring%20a%20warrior%20ethos%20back%20to%20the%20Pentagon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20also%20received%20support%20from%20many%20Republicans%20and%20veterans.%20Tim%20Kennedy%2C%20a%20retired%20Army%20Green%20Beret%20and%20mixed%20martial%20artist%2C%20has%20repeatedly%20advocated%20for%20Hegseth's%20candidacy%2C%20calling%20him%20%26quot%3Ban%20agent%20of%20change.%26quot%3B%20On%20Thursday%2C%20Senate%20Majority%20Leader%20John%20Thune%2C%20a%20South%20Dakota%20Republican%2C%20said%20that%20Hegseth%20would%20bring%20%26quot%3Ba%20warrior's%20perspective%20to%20the%20role%20of%20defense%20secretary%20and%20will%20provide%20much-needed%20fresh%20air%20at%20the%20Pentagon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHegseth's%20confirmation%20may%20bring%20radical%20changes%20to%20the%20Pentagon%20that%20had%20been%20resisted%20in%20Trump's%20first%20term.%20It%20was%20Hegseth%20who%20then%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpete-hegseth-advocated-pardons-of-us-troops-accused-of-war-crimes-2019-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadvised%3C%2Fa%3E%20Trump%20to%20pardon%20troops%20accused%20or%20convicted%20of%20war%20crimes%20over%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-listened-fox-host-pete-hegesth-over-his-secretary-defense-2019-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eobjections%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20top%20Pentagon%20leaders%20who%20worried%20this%20would%20erode%20the%20discipline%20and%20order%20in%20their%20ranks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225469%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pete%20Hegseth%20wearing%20a%20grey%20suit%20and%20camouflage%20print%20tie%20speaking%20into%20microphones%20held%20by%20reporters%20at%20Capitol%20Hill.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6793f714196626c40984fa9b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223646%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESenators%20questioned%20Hegseth%20about%20his%20personal%20life%2C%20views%2C%20and%20experience.%3Cp%3EAnna%20Moneymaker%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20rhetoric%20and%20background%2C%20Hegseth%20has%20been%20seen%20by%20lawmakers%20and%20officials%20as%20an%20unconventional%20pick.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHegseth%2C%20who%20served%20in%20Iraq%20and%20Afghanistan%2C%20was%20among%20a%20group%20of%20National%20Guard%20members%20who%20had%20their%20orders%20to%20secure%20then%20President-elect%20Joe%20Biden's%20inauguration%20revoked%20after%20the%20January%206%20insurrection%20due%20to%20controversy%20over%20his%20tattoo%20of%20a%20Jerusalem%20cross%3B%20he%20also%20has%20a%20tattoo%20of%20a%20Christian%20motto%20that%20dates%20to%20the%20Crusades%20and%20has%20been%20adopted%20by%20the%20alt-right.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHegseth%20has%20also%20received%20backlash%20over%20his%20views%20of%20women%20serving%20in%20combat%20roles.%20During%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDoN5ovwB8s4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20podcast%20episode%20after%20Trump's%20reelection%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Hegseth%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20straight-up%20just%20saying%20we%20should%20not%20have%20women%20in%20combat%20roles%2C%26quot%3B%20arguing%20it%20hurt%20the%20military's%20readiness.%20At%20his%20confirmation%20hearing%20in%20January%2C%20he%20took%20a%20different%20tone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYes%2C%20women%20will%20have%20access%20to%20ground%20combat%20roles%2C%20given%20the%20standards%20remain%20high%2C%20and%20we'll%20have%20a%20review%20to%20ensure%20the%20standards%20have%20not%20been%20eroded%20in%20any%20one%20of%20these%20cases%2C%26quot%3B%20Hegseth%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20if%20he's%20confirmed%2C%20he'll%20initiate%20a%20review%20of%20gender-neutral%20standards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223220%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pete%20Hegseth%20wearing%20a%20black%20tuxedo%20talking%20to%20someone%20with%20people%20standing%20around%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6793f68c196626c40984fa67%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222153%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHegseth%20has%20said%20he%20wants%20to%20bring%20warrior%20ethos%20back%20to%20the%20Pentagon%20and%20will%20order%20a%20review%20of%20physical%20standards%20for%20military%20jobs.%3Cp%3EAndrew%20Harnik%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20also%20been%20grilled%20about%20his%20drinking%2C%20beliefs%20against%20diversity%2C%20equity%2C%20and%20inclusion%2C%20and%20his%20personal%20history.%20During%20a%20media%20blitz%20to%20shore%20up%20his%20struggling%20candidacy%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress%2F-back-embattled-hegseth-says-trump-told-keep-fighting-rcna182855%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evowed%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3Bthere%20won't%20be%20a%20drop%20of%20alcohol%20on%20my%20lips%26quot%3B%20while%20he's%20the%20SECDEF.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20November%2C%20sexual%20assault%20allegations%20against%20Hegseth%20from%20an%20incident%20in%202017%20were%20made%20public.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20Hegseth%20told%20police%20that%20the%20encounter%20was%20consensual%20and%20denied%20any%20wrongdoing%3B%20he%20was%20never%20criminally%20charged.%20In%20November%2C%20he%20told%20reporters%20that%20the%20matter%20was%20fully%20investigated%20and%20he'd%20been%20cleared.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHegseth%2C%20an%20avowed%20opponent%20of%20the%20Defense%20Department's%20efforts%20to%20diversify%20its%20disproportionately%20white%20workforce%2C%20suggests%20major%20changes%20may%20be%20in%20store%20beyond%20the%20removal%20of%20any%20DEI%20or%20so-called%C2%A0%26quot%3Bwoke%26quot%3B%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20selection%20by%20Trump%20is%20also%20a%20sign%20the%20White%20House%20is%20focused%20on%20purging%20the%20military's%20top%20ranks%20of%20purported%C2%A0%26quot%3Bwoke%20generals%2C%26quot%3B%20along%20the%20lines%20of%20the%C2%A0%26quot%3Bwarrior%20board%26quot%3B%20reviews%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fpolitics%2Fnational-security%2Ftrump-draft-executive-order-would-create-board-to-purge-generals-7ebaa606%3Fmod%3Dnational-security_news_article_pos3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst%20reported%20by%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3