ledged%20to%20spend%20%24500%20billion%20building%20AI%20data%20centers%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOracle%20founder%20and%20CTO%20Larry%20Ellison%2C%20who%20joined%20Trump%2C%20OpenAI%20CEO%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-trump-stargate-build-agi-us-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESam%20Altman%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20SoftBank%20CEO%20Masayoshi%20Son%20at%20the%20briefing%2C%20said%20the%20first%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fproject-stargate-ai-deepseek-donald-trump-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStargate%3C%2Fa%3E%20data%20centers%20are%20currently%20being%20built%20in%20Abilene%2C%20Texas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20been%20working%20with%20OpenAI%20for%20a%20while%20and%20Masa%20for%20a%20while.%20The%20data%20centers%20are%20actually%20under%20construction%20%E2%80%94%20the%20first%20of%20them%20are%20under%20construction%20in%20Texas%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ellison.%20%26quot%3BEach%20building%20is%20a%20half%20million%20square%20feet.%20There%20are%2010%20buildings%20currently%20being%20built%2C%20but%20that%20will%20expand%20to%2020%20and%20other%20locations%20beyond%20the%20Abilene%20location%2C%20which%20is%20our%20first%20location.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELittle%20else%20has%20been%20revealed%20about%20Stargate.%20Registration%20forms%20filed%20with%20the%20Texas%20Department%20of%20Licensing%20and%20Regulation%20for%20a%20data%20center%20development%20in%20Abilene%20matching%20Ellison's%20description%20of%20Stargate%20give%20some%20insight%20into%20the%20cost%20of%20building%20the%20data%20centers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20development%20is%20registered%20with%20the%20TDLR%20under%20the%20name%20%26quot%3BProject%20Ludicrous%2C%26quot%3B%20located%20at%20an%20address%20attached%20to%20the%20Lancium%20Clean%20Campus%20%E2%80%94%20a%201%2C000-acre%20site%20in%20Abilene%20owned%20by%20energy%20tech%20company%20Lancium.%20The%20owner%20of%20Project%20Ludicrous%20is%20listed%20as%20Abilene%20DC%201%20LLC%2C%20an%20affiliate%20of%20data%20center%20development%20startup%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-ai-gpu-chips-demand-artificial-intelligence-debt-investing-cloud-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECrusoe%3C%2Fa%3E.%20According%20to%20the%20Texas%20state%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcomptroller.texas.gov%2Ftaxes%2Fdata-centers%2Fdata-center-lists.php%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecomptroller's%20records%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Oracle%20is%20the%20occupant%20of%20the%20data%20center%20owned%20by%20Abilene%20DC%201%2C%20LLC%2C%20located%20at%20the%20Lancium%20Clean%20Campus%20in%20Abilene.%20A%20Texas-based%20Oracle%20employee%20is%20also%20listed%20as%20the%20tenant%20contact%20for%20Project%20Ludicrous%20in%20the%20TDLR%20filings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%20July%20and%20December%202024%2C%20agents%20for%20Project%20Ludicrous%20filed%20four%20different%20TDLR%20filings%20for%20two%20buildings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConstruction%20on%20the%20first%20building%2C%20a%20482%2C000-square-foot%20one-story%20%26quot%3Bdata%20hall%26quot%3B%20estimated%20to%20cost%20%24292%20million%2C%20began%20in%20June%202024%20and%20is%20scheduled%20to%20be%20completed%20by%20May%2030%2C%202025.%20The%20estimate%20also%20includes%20plans%20for%20a%20guard%20house%2C%20fire%20pump%20building%2C%20and%20mechanical%20and%20electrical%20enclosures.%20A%20second%20filing%20for%20the%20building%2C%20made%20in%20September%2C%20indicates%20that%20tenant%20improvements%20costing%20%24140%20million%20began%20in%20December%20and%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20completed%20by%20September%2015%2C%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20second%20building%20registered%20under%20Project%20Ludicrous%2C%20a%20484%2C960-square-foot%20%26quot%3B1-story%20data%20center%26quot%3B%20with%20a%20cost%20estimate%20of%20%24292%20million%2C%20went%20under%20construction%20in%20September%20and%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20completed%20in%20one%20year%2C%20the%20filings%20said.%20Tenant%20improvements%2C%20expected%20to%20begin%20in%20March%20and%20be%20completed%20by%20December%2024%2C%20are%20estimated%20at%20%24384%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20San%20Antonio%20Express-News%20previously%20reported%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.expressnews.com%2Fbusiness%2Farticle%2Ftrump-ai-partnership-texas-projects-20047850.php%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eon%20these%20filings%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELancium%2C%20the%20landowner%2C%20first%20struck%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdevelopabilene.com%2F2024%2F11%2F19%2Fthe-development-corporation-of-abilene-city-of-abilene-and-taylor-county-announce-expanded-development-within-lanciums-clean-campus-through-crusoes-998000-square-foot-data-center%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edevelopment%20deal%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20the%20city%20of%20Abilene%20in%202021%20for%20what%20it%20calls%20the%20Lancium%20Clean%20Campus.%20The%20site%20was%20initially%20meant%20to%20power%20bitcoin%20mines%20with%20renewable%20energy%20generation%2C%20although%20that%20never%20came%20to%20fruition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20November%2C%20Crusoe%20announced%20plans%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcrusoe.ai%2Fnewsroom%2Fcrusoe-blue-owl-capital-primary-digital-joint-venture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%243.4%20billion%20data%20center%20development%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20Lancium%20Clean%20Campus%20and%20said%20it%20had%20already%20fully%20leased%20the%20space%20to%20a%20%26quot%3BFortune%20100%20hyperscale%20tenant%2C%26quot%3B%20with%20occupancy%20expected%20to%20begin%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Information%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D08f73f3dcd6c3cba0d9ca805dde0e97571b2817b7be04db63533e67dc3dcc8f7%26postID%3D6793a64922e74339bb4d0eec%26postSlug%3Dtexas-stargate-data-center-build-cost-2025-1%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.theinformation.com%252Farticles%