Irfan%20at%20a%20promotional%20event%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShami%20always%20provides%20honest%20feedback%20to%20the%20team%20management%2C%20and%20decisions%20are%20made%20through%20mutual%20communication.%20Recovery%20at%20the%20highest%20level%20takes%20time%2C%20especially%20after%20playing%20consistently.%20I%20believe%20he%20and%20the%20team%20management%20will%20make%20the%20right%20call%20at%20the%20right%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20undergone%20surgery%20and%20rehab%20following%20an%20ankle%20injury%20sustained%20during%20the%202023%20ODI%20World%20Cup%2C%20where%20he%20finished%20as%20India's%20top%20wicket-taker%2C%20Shami%20had%20made%20an%20impressive%20return%20in%20domestic%20cricket%2C%20representing%20Bengal%20across%20all%20three%20formats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShami%20has%20been%20chosen%20in%20India's%20white-ball%20rubber%20squad%20against%20England%20consisting%20five%20T20Is%20and%20three%20ODIs%20which%20will%20act%20as%20a%20build%20up%20to%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20next%20month%2C%20where%20the%20team's%20pace%20spearhead%20Jasprit%20Bumrah's%20inclusion%20is%20subject%20to%20fitness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBumrah%20suffered%20a%20back%20niggle%20in%20the%20gruelling%20five-match%20Test%20series%20in%20Australia%20and%20could%20not%20bowl%20in%20the%20second%20innings%20of%20the%20fifth%20Test%20in%20Sydney%2C%20and%20in%20this%20context%20Shami's%20availability%20for%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20is%20crucial%20to%20India's%20prospects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIrfan%20also%20expressed%20concerns%20over%20the%20lack%20of%20a%20pace-bowling%20backup%20in%20the%20Champions%20Trophy-bound%20squad%2C%20suggesting%20that%20Mohammed%20Siraj%20could%20have%20been%20included%20given%20Bumrah's%20uncertain%20fitness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20need%20a%20backup%20pacer.%20Siraj%20could%20have%20been%20a%20good%20option.%20In%20Dubai%2C%20playing%20four%20spinners%20isn't%20viable.%20With%20Bumrah%20and%20Shami%20returning%20from%20injuries%2C%20it%20won't%20be%20easy%20for%20them%20straight%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20pacer%20like%20Siraj%20would%20have%20filled%20that%20gap.%20That%20said%2C%20we%20hope%20the%20selectors'%20choices%20perform%20well%2C%20and%20we%20should%20back%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIrfan%20also%20addressed%20the%20poor%20form%20of%20senior%20batters%20Rohit%20Sharma%20and%20Virat%20Kohli%20during%20India's%201-3%20series%20defeat%20in%20the%20Border-Gavaskar%20Trophy%20--%20India's%20first%20series%20loss%20in%20a%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20advised%20fans%20not%20to%20conflate%20the%20celebrated%20duo's%20Test%20struggles%20with%20their%20prospects%20in%20white-ball%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey'll%20start%20scoring%20runs%20in%20white-ball%20cricket%3B%20there's%20no%20doubt%20about%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Irfan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTest%20cricket%20is%20a%20different%20ball%20game%20altogether.%20Adjustments%20are%20needed%2C%20whether%20it's%20Virat%20managing%20deliveries%20outside%20the%20off-stump%20or%20Rohit%20finding%20his%20rhythm.%20ODI%20is%20their%20favourite%20format%2C%20and%20they'll%20bounce%20back%20strongly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20India's%20resilience%20during%20the%202003-04%20Australia%20tour%2C%20Irfan%20further%20shared%20a%20motivational%20anecdote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBack%20then%2C%20Dean%20Jones%20visited%20our%20dressing%20room%20and%20mentioned%20how%20outsiders%20thought%20our%20team%20environment%20was%20broken.%20But%20we%20showed%20unity%20on%20the%20field%20and%20drew%20the%20series%201-1.%20Indian%20cricket%20is%20always%20above%20individual%20concerns%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIrfan%20also%20stressed%20the%20importance%20of%20domestic%20cricket%2C%20urging%20players%20to%20participate%20regularly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20about%20playing%20domestic%20cricket%20but%20do%20not%20play%20a%20couple%20of%20matches%20just%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20it%20and%20show%20that%20you've%20played.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlaying%20regularly%20benefits%20both%20players%20and%20Indian%20cricket.%20For%20young%20players%2C%20competing%20against%20the%20likes%20of%20Kohli%20or%20Rohit%20at%20the%20domestic%20level%20can%20be%20a%20tremendous%20confidence%20boost%20as%20they%20would%20also%20raise%20their%20levels%20to%20bowl%20to%20them.%20Ultimately%2C%20Indian%20cricket%20gains%20from%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737769020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F0be70nho_rohit-gambhir-agarkar-pti_625x300_03_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-champions-trophy-2025%2Fisnt-viable-big-doubts-over-bccis-team-india-squad-for-champions-trophy-raised-7540950%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20former%20India%20all-rounder%20addressed%20the%20poor%20form%20of%20senior%20batters%20Rohit%20Sharma%20and%20Virat%20Kohli.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-champions-trophy-2025%2Fisnt-viable-big-doubts-over-bccis-team-india-squad-for-champions-trophy-raised-7540950%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Her%20grandfather%20drove%20trains%20to%20Auschwitz.%20My%20family%20was%20murdered%20there%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737768828000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F17de%2Flive%2F67f09910-da73-11ef-a37f-eba91255dc3d.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc863g9d6vyeo%232%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amie%2C%20a%20descendant%20of%20a%20Holo