0Kolt%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ocean%20surrounding%20the%20Gal%C3%A1pagos%20has%20just%20as%20much%20action%20as%20the%20islands%20themselves%2C%20and%20snorkeling%20and%20diving%20are%20the%20most%20popular%20ways%20to%20experience%20it.%20The%20protected%20marine%20reserve%20surrounding%20the%20islands%20is%20home%20to%20endemic%20species%20like%20the%20Gal%C3%A1pagos%20penguin%2C%20the%20only%20species%20of%20penguin%20found%20in%20the%20northern%20hemisphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0You%20may%20also%20be%20lucky%20enough%20to%20see%20the%20marine%20iguana%2C%20the%20only%20known%20swimming%20iguana%20in%20the%20world.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22833%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20marine%20iguana%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F650204db1afe8f0019e9cf19%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22625%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Gal%C3%A1pagos%20Islands%20are%20home%20to%20the%20only%20swimming%20iguanas.%3Cp%3EMarci%20Vaughn%20Kolt%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EVisit%20a%20coffee%20farm%20in%20the%20highlands%20of%20Santa%20Cruz%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rich%20volcanic%20soil%20of%20the%20Gal%C3%A1pagos%20Islands%20is%20ideal%20for%20growing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-the-best-instant-coffee-review-2022-2%5C%22%3Ecoffee%20beans%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Because%2097%25%20of%20the%20islands%20are%20within%20the%20national%20park%20and%20only%20a%20small%20part%20can%20be%20used%20for%20agricultural%20purposes%2C%20coffee%20production%20is%20limited.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20several%20coffee%20farms%20on%20Santa%20Cruz%20Island%20offer%20tours%20and%20tastings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EExperience%20local%20life%20in%20the%20town%20of%20Puerto%20Ayora%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222724%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C