e%20Gaza%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20confirmed%20it%20had%20received%20the%20list%20of%20names%20of%20the%20captives%2C%20and%20the%20Hostage%20and%20Missing%20Families%20Forum%20campaign%20group%20later%20named%20them%20as%20Karina%20Ariev%2C%20Daniella%20Gilboa%2C%20Naama%20Levy%20and%20Liri%20Albag.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlbag%20turned%2019%20while%20in%20captivity%2C%20while%20the%20other%20women%20are%20all%20now%2020%20years%20old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20four%20were%20taken%20captive%20from%20Nahal%20Oz%20military%20base%2C%20just%20a%20kilometre%20(less%20than%20a%20mile)%20from%20the%20Gaza%20border%2C%20during%20Hamas's%20October%207%20attack%20on%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20all%20goes%20according%20to%20plan%2C%20after%20Hamas%20releases%20the%20four%20women%20on%20Saturday%2C%20Israel%20should%20free%20a%20group%20of%20Palestinian%20prisoners%2C%20though%20neither%20side%20has%20specified%20how%20many%20they%20will%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPalestinian%20sources%20told%20AFP%20the%20exchange%20could%20happen%20before%20noon.%20According%20to%20the%20Israel%20Prison%20Service%2C%20some%20of%20them%20will%20be%20released%20to%20Gaza%2C%20with%20the%20rest%20to%20return%20to%20the%20occupied%20West%20Bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20exchange%20is%20part%20of%20a%20ceasefire%20agreement%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20in%20the%20Gaza%20war%2C%20which%20took%20effect%20on%20Sunday%20and%20saw%20three%20women%20hostages%20and%2090%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20freed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fragile%20truce%20is%20intended%20to%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20a%20permanent%20end%20to%20the%20war%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbu%20Obeida%2C%20the%20spokesman%20for%20the%20Ezzedine%20al-Qassam%20Brigades%2C%20Hamas's%20armed%20wing%2C%20said%20on%20Telegram%20that%20%26quot%3Bas%20part%20of%20the%20prisoners'%20exchange%20deal%2C%20the%20Qassam%20brigades%20decided%20to%20release%20tomorrow%20four%20women%20soldiers%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu's%20office%20confirmed%20it%20had%20received%20the%20names%20through%20mediators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBassem%20Naim%2C%20a%20member%20of%20Hamas's%20political%20bureau%20based%20in%20Qatar%2C%20on%20Friday%20told%20AFP%20that%20Palestinians%20displaced%20by%20the%20war%20to%20southern%20Gaza%20should%20be%20able%20to%20begin%20returning%20to%20the%20north%20of%20the%20devastated%20territory%20following%20the%20releases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20Egyptian-Qatari%20committee%20will%20oversee%20the%20implementation%20of%20this%20part%20of%20the%20agreement%20on%20the%20ground%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20displaced%20Gazans%20longed%20to%20return%20home%20after%20more%20than%20a%20year%20of%20war%2C%20many%20found%20only%20rubble%20where%20houses%20once%20stood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20if%20we%20thought%20about%20returning%2C%20there%20is%20no%20place%20for%20us%20to%20put%20our%20tents%20because%20of%20the%20destruction%2C%26quot%3B%20Theqra%20Qasem%2C%20a%20displaced%20woman%2C%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20'Eating%20away%20at%20us'%20-%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ceasefire%20agreement%2C%20brokered%20by%20Qatar%2C%20Egypt%20and%20the%20United%20States%20after%20months%20of%20fruitless%20negotiations%2C%20should%20be%20implemented%20in%20three%20phases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20who%20has%20claimed%20credit%20for%20the%20agreement%2C%20said%20Thursday%20he%20believed%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20deal%20should%20hold%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20first%2C%2042-day%20phase%2C%2033%20hostages%20Israel%20believes%20are%20still%20alive%20should%20be%20returned%20in%20exchange%20for%20around%201%2C900%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20held%20in%20Israeli%20jails.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20phase%20should%20see%20negotiations%20for%20a%20more%20permanent%20end%20to%20the%20war%2C%20while%20the%20last%20phase%20should%20see%20the%20reconstruction%20of%20Gaza%20and%20the%20return%20of%20the%20bodies%20of%20dead%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20swap%20on%20Sunday%20saw%20the%20release%20of%20Israeli%20hostages%20Emily%20Damari%2C%20Romi%20Gonen%20and%20Doron%20Steinbrecher.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHours%20later%2C%2090%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20were%20freed%20from%20Israeli%20jails%2C%20most%20of%20them%20women%20and%20minors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Israel%2C%20families%20of%20hostages%20held%20for%20more%20than%2015%20months%20in%20Gaza%20fear%20that%20the%20ceasefire%20could%20collapse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20worry%20and%20fear%20that%20the%20deal%20will%20not%20be%20implemented%20to%20the%20end%20is%20eating%20away%20at%20all%20of%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Vicky%20Cohen%2C%20the%20mother%20of%20hostage%20Nimrod%20Cohen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20these%20days%2C%20there%20are%20elements%20in%20the%20government%20who%20are%20doing%20everything%20in%20their%20power%20to%20torpedo%20the%20second%20phase.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20far-right%20members%20of%20Netanyahu's%20governing%20coalition%20opposed%20the%20deal%2C%20with%20firebrand%20Itamar%20Ben%20Gvir%20pulling%20his%20party%20out%20of%20the%20coalition%20in%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20Lebanon%20withdrawal%20delay%20-%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20their%202023%20attack%20on%20Israel%2C%20Hamas%20militants%20took%20251%20hostages%2C%2091%20of%20whom%20remain%20in%20Gaza%2C%20including%2034%20the%20Israeli%20military%20has%20confirmed%20are%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%2C%20the%20deadliest%20in%20Israel's%20history%2C%20resulted%20in%20the%20deaths%20of%201%2C210%20people%2C%20mostly%20civilians%2C%20according%20to%20an%20AFP%20tally%20based%20on%20official%20Israeli%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20retaliatory%20response%20has%20killed%20at%20least%2047%2C283%20people%20in%20Gaza%2C%20a%20majority%20civilians%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Hamas-run%20territory's%20heal