c-ruling-favouring-tiger-global-in-flipkart-stake-sale-125012401456_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Foreign%20Minister%20Engages%20US%2C%20Foreign%20Secretary%2C%20China%3A%20India's%20Balancing%20Act%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia's%20diplomacy%20stands%20out%20globally%20for%20its%20ability%20to%20balance%20ties%20between%20adversaries.%20The%20latest%20example%20of%20this%20is%20happening%20this%20week.%20As%20foreign%20minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20touches%20down%20in%20New%20Delhi%20after%20a%20five-day%20visit%20to%20the%20US%20for%20Donald%20Trump's%20inauguration%2C%20foreign%20secretary%20Vikram%20Misri%20heads%20to%20China%20to%20foster%20ties%20with%20Beijing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20ten%20days%20ago%2C%20during%20a%20visit%20to%20Spain%2C%20foreign%20minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20had%20said%20India%20is%20one%20of%20the%20very%20few%20countries%20in%20the%20world%20that%20can%20engage%20both%20Russia%20and%20Ukraine%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Israel%20and%20Iran.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20something%20very%2C%20very%20unique.%20And%20it%20is%20unique%20because%20if%20you%20look%20at%20the%20world%20today%2C%20it%20is%20a%20very%20polarised%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDonald%20Trump%20has%20threatened%20to%20impose%20hefty%20tariffs%20on%20China%20and%20even%20the%20BRICS%2B%20countries%2C%20which%20India%20is%20a%20member%20of%20as%20well.%20China%2C%20the%20world's%20second-largest%20economy%2C%20has%20warned%20that%20it%20will%20retaliate%2C%20should%20Washington%20actually%20follow%20through.%20President%20Trump%20has%20also%20targeted%20China%20over%20its%20presence%20in%20the%20Panama%20Canal%20and%20said%20the%20US%20will%20take%20control%20of%20the%20waterway%20even%20if%20it%20means%20involving%20the%20military.%20China%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20has%20warned%20Washington%20over%20its%20involvement%20with%20Taiwan.%20Both%20nations%20have%20sanctioned%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EENGAGING%20ALL%20SIDES%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20all%20this%2C%20India%2C%20which%20according%20to%20PM%20Modi%2C%20has%20%26quot%3Balways%20chosen%20the%20side%20of%20peace%26quot%3B%2C%20aims%20to%20engage%20all%20sides%20for%20positive%20and%20constructive%20outcomes.%20Earlier%20this%20week%2C%20S%20Jaishankar%20strengthened%20India-US%20bilateral%20ties%20when%20he%20met%20the%20US%20Secretary%20of%20State%20and%20National%20Security%20Adviser%20for%20their%20first%20foreign%20engagements%20after%20the%20Trump%20administration%20took%20over.%20As%20PM%20Modi's%20special%20envoy%2C%20Dr%20Jaishankar%20was%20also%20given%20the%20first%20seat%20at%20the%20US%20President's%20inauguration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20returned%20after%20concluding%20%26quot%3Ba%20very%20positive%26quot%3B%20visit%20to%20Washington%2C%20India's%20foreign%20secretary%20heads%20to%20Beijing%20to%20build%20the%20momentum%20in%20India-China%20ties%20following%20a%20meeting%20between%20PM%20Modi%20and%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20in%20Russia%20late-last%20year.%20Foreign%20Secretary%20Misri's%20visit%20was%20preceded%20by%20a%20visit%20by%20National%20Security%20Adviser%20Ajit%20Doval%20last%20month%20when%20he%20met%20Chinese%20foreign%20minister%20Wang%20Yi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EREBUILDING%20AFTER%20THE%20STORM%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20China%2C%20two%20of%20Asia's%20leading%20economies%20and%20the%20world's%20most%20populous%20nations%2C%20are%20working%20to%20boost%20bilateral%20ties%20after%20a%20four-and-a-half-year-long%20military%20standoff%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20or%20LAC%20brought%20ties%20to%20a%20grinding%20halt.%20After%20dozens%20of%20rounds%20of%20talks%20-%20both%20diplomatically%20and%20militarily%20-%20an%20agreement%20was%20reached%20and%20troops%20on%20both%20sides%20pulled%20back%20from%20the%20buffer%20zones%2C%20returning%20the%20status%20quo-ante.%20This%20happened%20within%20a%20week%20of%20PM%20Modi%20and%20Xi%20Jinping%20announcing%20it%20during%20a%20meeting%20in%20Russia%20late%20last%20year.%20Following%20this%2C%20Chinese%20and%20Indian%20foreign%20and%20defence%20ministers%20also%20met%20each%20other%20on%20multilateral%20occasions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Ajit%20Doval%2C%20foreign%20secretary%20Vikram%20Misri's%20will%20be%20the%20second%20high-level%20visit%20by%20an%20Indian%20official%20to%20Beijing%20in%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20WELCOME%20FROM%20BEIJING%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20has%20welcomed%20Foreign%20Secretary%20Vikram%20Misri's%20visit%20this%20weekend%20and%20sounded%20positive%20about%20its%20outcome.%20%26quot%3BWe%20welcome%20Foreign%20Secretary%20Shri%20Vikram%20Misri's%20travel%20to%20China%20for%20the%20meeting%20of%20the%20Foreign%20Secretary-Vice%20Minister%20mechanism%20between%20China%20and%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20Chinese%20Foreign%20Ministry%20Spokesperson%20Mao%20Ning%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20also%20said%20that%20%26quot%3BForeign%20Secretary%20Vikram%20Misri%20will%20be%20visiting%20Beijing%20on%20January%2026%20and%2027%20for%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20Foreign%20Secretary-Vice%20Minister%20mechanism%20between%20India%20and%20China.%20The%20resumption%20of%20this%20bilateral%20mechanism%20flows%20from%20the%20agreement%20at%20the%20leadership%20level%20to%20discuss%20the%20next%20steps%20for%20India-China%20relations%2C%20including%20in%20the%20political%2C%20economic%2C%20and%20people-to-people%20domains.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETHE%20AGENDA%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20bilateral%20issues%20such%20as%20boundary%20talks%2C%20maintaining%20peace%20along%20the%20LAC%2C%20the%20building%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20dam%20on%20the%20Brahmaputra%2C%20resumption%20of%20the%20Kailash%20Mansarovar%20Yatra%2C%20people-to-people%20ties%2C%20resuming