20with%20the%20students%20in%20front%20of%20the%20renovated%20school%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%E2%80%99s%20approach%20is%20methodical%20and%20deeply%20rooted%20in%20community%20engagement.%20Before%20beginning%20any%20project%2C%20they%20conduct%20thorough%20research%20and%20consult%20with%20principals%20and%20teachers%20to%20identify%20the%20school%E2%80%99s%20specific%20needs.%20By%20addressing%20these%20needs%20comprehensively%2C%20ASKK%20ensures%20that%20its%20efforts%20lead%20to%20long-term%20benefits%20rather%20than%20temporary%20fixes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20outcome%20is%20undeniably%20positive%2C%20the%20journey%20has%20not%20been%20without%20challenges.%20Funding%20for%20ASKK%E2%80%99s%20initiatives%20primarily%20comes%20from%20friends%20and%20family%2C%20with%20the%20founders%E2%80%99%20parents%20providing%20unwavering%20support.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20never%20think%20about%20profits%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Mohammad.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20satisfaction%20of%20creating%20change%20in%20the%20community%20keeps%20us%20going.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20goal%20is%20to%20create%20a%20safe%20and%20stimulating%20environment%20that%20encourages%20students%20to%20stay%20in%20school%20and%20pursue%20their%20education%20enthusiastically%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Mohammad.%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ve%20seen%20how%20a%20positive%20atmosphere%20can%20make%20a%20significant%20difference%20in%20a%20child%E2%80%99s%20motivation%20to%20learn%2C%20and%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20do%20so%20in%20whatever%20capacity%20we%20can.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3B%20All%20images%20courtesy%20ASKK%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737519069000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Ffile-44_11zon-1737294072.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D398965%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20Tamil%20Nadu%E2%80%99s%20ru